snippet.title: I Added a HUGE Ramp to My Racing Game
snippet.description:
Wishlist Apex Rush on Steam! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2638250/Apex_Rush/
Vote for what I should build here! - https://discord.gg/VEMAZeD
Today we're back with Part 3 of me making my first racing game in Unreal Engine 5! This is one of my favorite videos so far, since I added a lot of cool things to the level! But as always, there is still more to add...

*The game is not available to play yet but I will release a playtest version of this level once it's done!

I hope you all enjoy this video, Drop a LIKE & Subscribe if you're new! 

My Clothing Brand: https://nosleep.co/
